## {{ rule.title }}

IRS Publication 514's treaty re-sourcing worksheet ends at line 21: the additional [Form 1116](https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-1116) credit equals `min(line 19, line 20c)` — the lesser of the U.S. tax above the treaty floor and the residual German tax on the same dividends. [Form 1116](https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-1116) line 33 then caps the credit at the remaining nonrefundable room.

