- [Pub. 514](https://www.irs.gov/publications/p514) **line 21** — `min(line 19, line 20c)`: **{{ add.worksheet_line_21_additional_credit_usd | money(currency="USD") }}**
- Final additional FTC after [Form 1116](https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-1116) line 33 nonrefundable cap: **{{ add.treaty_resourcing_additional_ftc_usd | money(currency="USD") }}**
- Regular tax after baseline FTC + treaty re-sourcing: **{{ add.regular_tax_after_ftc_and_treaty_resourcing_usd | money(currency="USD") }}**

The additional credit feeds the final allowed FTC at US25-19 and reduces the regular tax that the payments calculation at US25-21 uses.

